sequenceDiagram
    participant R as Researcher machine
    participant O as Opal / Rock
    participant N as SuperNode (Python)

    Note over R: Generate CA + server certs
    R ->> R: Encode ca_cert_pem as Base64

    R ->> O: flowerEnsureSuperNodeDS(..., B64-encoded cert) [HTTPS]

    O ->> O: Decode Base64, write ca.pem to disk

    O ->> N: Start flower-supernode with --root-certificates ca.pem
    N ->> R: gRPC TLS handshake (verified)
